response.overview: Take a magical journey with this episode of the popular Real Wheels children's series that showcases the show's most memorable tunes in a sing-along extravaganza. The adventure begins aboard a rushing railroad, then continues with a stint on a fearsome fire truck barreling through the city streets on the way to douse a conflagration. The momentum slows as the excitement peaks during a trip through a construction site, courtesy of a bulldozer.
response.title: Real Wheels: Rockin' Real Wheels
